description: Make these easy fish taco wraps filled with coleslaw and aioli for a quick lunch or dinner. All you need is four ingredients to make this speedy meal.
keywords: Taco,Fish,Tree nut free,Video,Dinner Made Easy,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Easy Fish Taco Wraps Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 225g Birds Eye Deli lightly crumbed lemon pepper fish
10 Old El Paso regular flour tortillas

recipeInstructions.text: Cook fish according to packet instructions. Transfer to a plate and flake into large pieces.
Meanwhile, heat a large chargrill pan over high heat. Cook tortillas for 30 seconds on each side or until charred and warmed through. Wrap in foil to keep warm.
Place coleslaw in a bowl and top with a little aioli.
Top tortillas with slaw, fish and remaining aioli. Season and serve.
